Package: jigsawR
Type: Package
Title: R Translations of JavaScript Jigsaw Puzzle Generators
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Philipp Thoss [aut, cre] (0000-0002-4672-2792)
Maintainer: Philipp Thoss <ph.thoss@gmx.de>
Authors@R: 
    person("Philipp", "Thoss", , "ph.thoss@gmx.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4672-2792"))
Description: R translations of Draradech's JavaScript jigsaw puzzle generators
    with enhanced puzzle visualization capabilities. Supports rectangular,
    hexagonal, concentric, Voronoi, and random shape puzzles with high-quality
    SVG output, gradient backgrounds, and configurable piece separation.
    Direct ports of the original JavaScript algorithms maintaining mathematical
    precision while adding R-based visualization and tessellation capabilities.
